  "description": "The Charlsensideas Mod adds cool things to Minecrtaft that just come to my Mind.",
  "body": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"104\" /></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Note: This mod is no longer maintained. .</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yjM7QOx.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"687\" height=\"172\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzBj08FS4tDr3Lyf9zWM3kg\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzBj08FS4tDr3Lyf9zWM3kg</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">https://thecharlsen.github.io</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>IF PLAYED ON SERVER:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Make sure you have the mod in your local mod folder and in the server mod folder.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>FEATURES:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">The Charlsensideas Mod has Features like the MusicPlayer which opens an interface when rightclicked where you can select music that you want to hear.&nbsp;<strong>(NOTE: The MusicPlayer is in Beta).</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">There are also new weapons which have a custom Model coming.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">GO into the new TENEBRIS dimension with tourmaline bricks and weird water!<br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Adds 2 new Biomes and Trees.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Cool Gadgets will nto much affect the User Experience.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #993300;\">Enjoy the Mod</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #ffcc00;\">Developed by Charlsen</span></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
